<section class="slider_section">
    <div id="myCarousel" class="carousel slide banner-main" data-ride="carousel">
        <div class="carousel-inner">
            <div class="carousel-item active">
                <img class="first-slide" src="/assets/banner.jpg" alt="First slide">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="carousel-caption relative">
                        <h1>Welcome to Our Library!</h1>
                        <p>We are dedicated to providing you with a vast collection of resources to fuel your passion <br>for reading and learning. Our online offers a diverse array of books, all accessible <br>from the comfort of your home.</p>
                        <p class="collapse" id="moreContent">
                            Whether you’re looking for the latest bestseller, classic literature, or educational <br> materials, we have something for everyone.
                        </p>
                        <a class="main_bt" href="#!" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#moreContent" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="moreContent">Read More</a>

                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img class="second-slide" src="/assets/banner.jpg" alt="Second slide">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="carousel-caption relative">
                        <h1>Explore Our Extensive Catalog.</h1>
                        <p>With user-friendly search and filter options, finding your next great read has never been easier.<br>Our library is regularly updated with new titles across various genres, <br>ensuring that you have access to the latest releases and timeless classics.</p>
                        <p class="collapse" id="moreContent2">Join our community of avid readers and discover the joy of reading at your own pace.</p>
                        <a class="main_bt" href="#!" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#moreContent2" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="moreContent2">Read More</a>

                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img class="third-slide" src="/assets/banner.jpg" alt="Third slide">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="carousel-caption relative">
                        <h1>Get Started Today!</h1>
                        <p>Signing up is simple and free. Once you become a member, you can access our entire collection, <br>reserve books, and receive personalized recommendations tailored to your reading preferences.</p>
                        <p class="collapse" id="moreContent3">Join us on this exciting journey and let the world of literature open up new horizons for you!</p>
                        <a class="main_bt" href="#!" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#moreContent3" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="moreContent3">Read More</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#myCarousel" role="button" data-slide="prev">
            <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
        </a>
        <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#myCarousel" role="button" data-slide="next">
            <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
        </a>
    </div>
</section>
